items.sentence: Tom told me he thought Mary would be curious.
The only person Tom knows in Australia is me.
I told Tom that he shouldn't go to Australia.
I added Tom's name to the list of candidates.
Did you read the notice that was on the wall?
Do you remember what we have to do on Monday?
Mary said that she'd never leave her husband.
Mary never received the flowers Tom sent her.
I forgot to tell Tom I couldn't speak French.
I knew you wouldn't go to Australia with Tom.
